### Execute command on a specific server
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/command
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "d8821d937aad4f5399f72c47fc8e3cf5",
  "targetType": "server",
  "command": "say Hello from the API!"
}

### Execute command on all servers in a group
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/command
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "lobby",
  "targetType": "group",
  "command": "say Maintenance starting in 5 minutes!"
}

### Execute command on all servers and proxies
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/command
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "all",
  "targetType": "all",
  "command": "say Global announcement!"
}
